summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2811 for the improvement of Dearborn Street, form the existing pavement at Fifth Avenue South and Seattle Boulevard to a connectin with the existing pavement at the east margin of Seventh Avenue South; all in the City of Seattle under Ordinance No. 33753, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
